Yes, you're all right! Choose what you will; it's all the same. You'll be all right anywhere. But look here: give up visiting those Kurdgins and lead- ing that sort of life. It suits you so badly all this debauchery, dissipation, and the rest of it!" 
"What would you have, my dear fellow?" answered Pierre, shrugging his shoulders. "Women, my dear fellow; women!"
